Power Input
===========

|Product| can be powered by a wide range of input voltages: |vin_rng| DC. It is a **3 Pin, 3.81mm screw terminal** connector.
The polarity and the pinout is clearly marked on the housing of the |productP| version, as shown in the figures below.

.. rst-class:: text-center

    |power_img|

    *Power Input*
